## Have a great project?
We would love to discover it and help you make it happen!
Click below and fill out the request form. A Cover Styl Expert will contact you as soon as possible to discuss your ideas and help you find the perfect product based on your surfaces and requirements.

attributes.playstoreDownloadText: Download on the Google Play Store

attributes.Name: Glitter
attributes.Description: Want an interior with disco inspirations? Sparkling originality? Count on our Glitter range and its glam & glossy and unique looks! Whether they are colorful or not, your pieces will shine brightly once combined with optimal lighting.

seo.metaDescription: Looking for a disco-inspired interior? Count on our Pailleté range and its glamorous, glossy looks.
